Step1: Copy the column that you want to convert to CSV
Step2: Paste the values in Word
Step3: Click Ctrl + H 
Step4: In the Find Box, type "^p"
Step5: In the Replace Box, type ","
Step6: Hit Replace All to convert the values to comma separated values
Step7: Copy the data and paste in Notepad and save with the extension .csv
Step8: You're done
